 Galvatron looked at the queen. "Hm very interesting." he snapped his finger 
hard and they clicked with a sound. "I wanted to test Prime. Me and him have 
yet to say our hellos since his and my return. I  like your ideas on the 
preds. I will prove myself to you in battle and hope to win your trust and 
one day become your war general. I have the collected sparks of Apocalypse, 
Proto1000, and Death. I also hold Dba from bots known as Zardus, Cerberus, 
Energon, Drill Bit, and Dark Mouse. I hope I will help win the beast wars for 
the destrons and take pleasure in serving you. But only you. I dont answer to 
Unicron."

--part1_ca.fb4fa46.279a4c79_boundary
